{"tid":268084,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"ios單機武俠game","createTime":"2017-06-02T17:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T14:49:11.000Z","uid":12593,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"503e818257b1f07bbc3ae9c87aff6eb95daca535","tid":268084,"uid":12593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:56:18.000Z","msg":"純分享暫時覺得幾好玩嘅手機單機武俠game，大多都要畀$8買<br />\n<br />\n首先係論劍，一隻係由純文字（包括動作、表情）組合嘅遊戲。個人覺得悶悶地<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/014304_8dc3c3907186833f4567b733de22b6f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F014304_8dc3c3907186833f4567b733de22b6f5.jpg&h=02a107ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以下遊戲大多都係簡體字為主！</span></span><br />\n首先，係群俠傳系列，佢有好多唔同版本，小弟淨係玩咗以下三款，其中值得一提嘅係超級群俠傳可以自己合武功，而佢亦都係作者最新嘅作品<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/014648_d1b29ac59ac71615f76632cc4291c4a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F014648_d1b29ac59ac71615f76632cc4291c4a8.jpg&h=d6d80ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/014659_18e3784588332b913648449c0c5a61bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F014659_18e3784588332b913648449c0c5a61bd.jpg&h=9d58297d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/014734_46b1735a5e7b886aa1138855b5b26450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F014734_46b1735a5e7b886aa1138855b5b26450.jpg&h=d1e2e0ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後，就係我依家沈迷緊嘅劍俠恩仇錄，佢都係以簡體字為主，係一個半單機嘅形式（淨係有排名同武鬥場）唯一就係bugs好多，而官方都唔係點理<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/015032_77aad559a3643922e9a3decff71db873.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F015032_77aad559a3643922e9a3decff71db873.jpg&h=a4e86741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟並非打手，淨係想分享下啲單機武俠遊戲畀巴打試下，如果有啲可以聯機嘅，希望巴打可以介紹下畀我玩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ced23ed434d2013d41eab108f4de399de1f613","tid":268084,"uid":6953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"頭三隻邊隻最好玩？ 劇情係咪一樣ga"},{"pid":"aa2c3acdfe4f341cee18ca80a57f79ce5ea7bd3b","tid":268084,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:54:57.000Z","msg":"第一個垃圾<br />\n我不如玩放置江湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9634f94423724bb78101170c5295cc969d767cac","tid":268084,"uid":12593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭三隻邊隻最好玩？ 劇情係咪一樣ga</blockquote><br />\n金庸群俠隻隻都差唔多"}]}